  "detailed_description": "After falling asleep in the cinema, you wake up in a movie you've seen so many times before. Use your detective skills to solve the mystery of the missing film crew and finish the movie. There are strange sound waves that appear to be keeping everyone trapped in this cryptic world. <br>Maybe these sound waves are your way out! Explore the diverse world of <strong>Shutterville</strong>, inspired by horror <strong>B-movies</strong>.<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 80 game scenes<br></li><li>21 mini games<br></li><li>New silhouette matching mode<br></li><li>Original soundtrack</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "After falling asleep in the cinema, you wake up in a movie you've seen so many times before. Use your detective skills to solve the mystery of the missing film crew and finish the movie. There are strange sound waves that appear to be keeping everyone trapped in this cryptic world. <br>Maybe these sound waves are your way out! Explore the diverse world of <strong>Shutterville</strong>, inspired by horror <strong>B-movies</strong>.<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 80 game scenes<br></li><li>21 mini games<br></li><li>New silhouette matching mode<br></li><li>Original soundtrack</li></ul>",
